{"tid":2007730,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"X Mini Supa呢隻小喇叭，終於滿足到我想起睡房建立小電影欣賞室既想法","createTime":"2020-05-08T13:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T16:16:37.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c31864e4305e24ef2ef129ef3abae19364fa7f57","tid":2007730,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t5hBUTe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft5hBUTe.jpg&h=f4d99fcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先前出左個post關於我想買對喇叭仔代替係骰仔咁大嘅房間擺條比例上太誇張既soundbar，感激介紹我買呢隻小喇叭既巴打，我上網研究過好多開箱片開箱文都大讚，買返黎真係覺得好值，佢既模擬環繞聲好包圍，聲量足夠，低頻剛剛好唔會太誇張高頻都掩蓋埋。<br />\n<br />\n原價過千而我買八舊水，原來都已經推出左兩年多係間舖既1001隻，我就係搵唔到有其他咁多好評既產品先要搵呢隻舊野，好彩搵得到亦不負所望。<br />\n<br />\n不過缺點始終只係藍牙小喇叭， 除咗藍牙就只有3.5mm Aux in， 而且只得一個開關掣同旋鈕，調較上比較麻煩， 如果有賣光纖輸入什至hdmi再加個遙控仔，咁就very good喇"},{"pid":"b54c0367a61abc721e8e98daa93395971f9d10a0","tid":2007730,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:15:15.000Z","msg":"What is this?"},{"pid":"cd5ce9904b178ef7ae545fc468fe808653a0de1f","tid":2007730,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b54c0367a61abc721e8e98daa93395971f9d10a0","tid":2007730,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:15:15.000Z","msg":"What is this?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:23:20.000Z","msg":"藍牙小喇叭"},{"pid":"ae6c251b728ec23129043ce8d42d34ff5bad3f76","tid":2007730,"uid":340074,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"周杰倫好型"},{"pid":"87519190a926b1a7901a7ea5cf72de15c4513763","tid":2007730,"uid":25170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T16:16:37.000Z","msg":"之前都買咗呢隻<br />\n會有少少類似電流聲嘅嘈音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主試下你嗰隻 聽真啲/擺近啲耳仔睇下有無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}